<plot>Horace Pentothine, a man whose chin was left in the shape of a knife due to a rare trombone accident as a child, is tormented into a life of crime. In desperation, trying to raise enough money for plastic surgery to reshape his chin, he robs a bank, and winds up going down in the annals of crime for committing one of the most unusual crimes in history.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?208160</url></doc>
